<plot>1979. Mamma is turning sixty, which calls for a celebration. The day before her birthday, her two elder sons and their wives return to her home in a narrow valley in Northern Troms. Their younger brother, given to drink and still living at home, brings out some moonshine. Mamma has fallen asleep in the combi camper. The party takes off completely. And while hard liquor is being poured down open gullets, big brother's Sami jacket emerges from the closet. Conditions are ripe for a quarrel about origin and identity.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?250625</url></doc>
